---
---

<section id="about" aria-labelledby="about-label">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="section-label" id="about-label">About</p>
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-photo">
        <img src="/photo.jpeg" alt="Photo of Agnislav Onufriichuk" width="280" height="340" />
      </div>
      <div class="about-text">
        <h2>From code to<br />culture.</h2>
        <p>I'm a hands-on engineering leader who's spent nearly two decades at the intersection of building software and building teams. I've led orgs from 3 to 40 engineers, <strong>shipped MVPs to production in under a month</strong>, and established delivery processes that let teams operate without bottlenecks or bus factors.</p>
        <p>I'm not the kind of leader who stops writing code. I still refactor core modules, evaluate testing frameworks, and introduce tooling — like bringing <strong>AI-assisted development workflows</strong> to my teams. But my real impact is in <strong>translating business goals into engineering execution</strong>: architecture decisions, hiring, process design, and getting products to market.</p>
        <p>I've done this across industries — crypto wallets, streaming platforms, travel marketplaces, and e-commerce — always in cross-cultural, distributed environments.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 280px 1fr;
    gap: 80px;
  }

  .about-photo {
    width: 280px;
    height: 340px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .about-photo img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: top;
    display: block;
  }

  .about-text h2 {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .about-text p {
    color: var(--muted);
    max-width: 520px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .about-text p :global(strong) {
    color: var(--fg);
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 32px;
    }
    .about-photo {
      width: 100%;
      height: 200px;
    }
  }
</style>
